window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Elorion has just finished a VR gaming session to find a monster waiting for him. With 19 other students who have also been kidnapped, he is now subject to the whims of a thousand year old succubus, and he must survive deep under the Earth in the lost realm of the Underworld.&nbsp;</p> <p>Gifted with the ability to use magic and advance in power, he is given an ultimatum: Level up or die!</p>"; 
